casebody.data:
Jo-Louise BAKER, Respondent,
v.
John A. LISCONISH, Respondent, Santo Heating and Air Conditioning, Inc., Appellant. Motion No: 2018-216 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided May 1, 2018

Motion to dismiss appeal granted and appeal dismissed, with $400 costs and $100 costs of motion, upon the ground that the order appealed from does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
